{"tid":1809271,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"藝人方力申獲委任為旅發局新成員","createTime":"2020-01-03T03:25:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-03T03:45:52.000Z","uid":277339,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6680ac9741bc8a23ee9140f56c1495968336dd2e","tid":1809271,"uid":277339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T03:25:51.000Z","msg":"政府公布委任藝人兼前港隊泳手方力申，出任旅遊發展局新成員，任期由今年元旦日起，為期兩年。<br />\n<br />\n商務及經濟發展局發言人表示，歡迎方力申加入旅發局，有信心他和其他成員在不同界別的專業知識及豐富經驗，可以協助旅發局進一步推廣香港。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1245411&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1245411%26csid%3D261_341&d=GDp31xM3xvXFOTrKf8Ol7LvH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=082f7b0d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1245411&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"854031736c077c4e950f9e349dfa86666c979d68","tid":1809271,"uid":48362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T03:36:18.000Z","msg":"万刀甲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3ab71b3ffa23a47fca25c02d259a7b2fbf8b9b6","tid":1809271,"uid":175623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T03:45:52.000Z","msg":"暖氣軍師收皮啦，捉唔捉鬼係現場決定<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eJeHyS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eJeHyS</a>"}]}